Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tanjiro...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take up your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's something you must cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's something...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must cut.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's something I must cut...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in order to wake up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think I know what it is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.39,0:00:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't hesitate! Do it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have to do it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My death in this dream\Nwill lead me to reality!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other words...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}what I have to cut is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:00:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my own neck!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must be the incarnations\Nof this boy's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The air is so clear, and it feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that his spiritual core?\NWhy are you showing it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring me here\Nbecause I was searching for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Even though I was trying to destroy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}EPISODE 4:\NINSULT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck is his spiritual core?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this realm\Nof the subconscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that creepy naked boar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, this is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing\Nin the realm of the subconscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid naked boar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's pitch-dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's pitch-dark,\Nand I can't see a thing. Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that blond brat's\Nrealm of subconscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to grope around\Nto find his spiritual core?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:04:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's a guy doing in here?\NDamn you, parasite!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one's allowed in here but Nezuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm so going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Nezuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who the heck knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then... Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nezuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right. I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nezuko! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nezuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zenitsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rengoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who are these people?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're all connected\Nby the wrists with ropes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rope...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's burned off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nezuko's burning blood did it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's faint, but I'm picking up\Na demon's scent, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This smell... The ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew it. It's giving off\Na faint demon smell, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}TOKYO - MUGEN
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We were put to sleep\Nwhen our tickets were punched.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This must be a demon's work!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did he unleash such a potent Blood Demon Art\Nusing just this faint scent?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know why...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I have a feeling that I shouldn't sever\Nthis rope with my Nichirin Sword.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nezuko! Do me a favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to burn off everyone's rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zenitsu! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Zenitsu!\NYou have to wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Inosuke! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There, there... Sorry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did a great job, Nezuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}It's no good. These two won't wake up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What can I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rengoku—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is a demon controlling her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you guys,\Nwe won't be able to have dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is she acting of her own free will?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This man, too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're awake,\Nyou'd better help us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You may have tuberculosis or whatever,\Nbut if you don't do your job,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell him, and then,\Nhe won't show you any dreams, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he the one\Nwho was connected to me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tuberculosis...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's sick.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Poor man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What this demon did is unforgivable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He took advantage of their weak souls!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You want to stay\Ninside a happy dream, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to stay inside my dream, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If only this was the dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until I touched his heart...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was willing to hurt others...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if it meant I could escape\Nfrom the pain of this illness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nezuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The smell is overpowering!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So heavy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The demon's scent is so strong\Neven in this strong wind!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was I asleep in such an awful scent?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if each car was closed off and airtight,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe I was!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was useless!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The demon's upwind...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he in the first car?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nezuko, don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go wake everyone up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You could've stayed asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}DREAM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}LOWER ONE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}DEMON SLAYER: KIMETSU NO YAIBA\NMUGEN TRAIN ARC
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:12:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}DEMON SLAYER: KIMETSU NO YAIBA\NMUGEN TRAIN ARC
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I show you a sweet dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could've shown you a dream\Nwhere your family was being slaughtered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you have liked that one better?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not.\NToo distressing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, next...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I show you a dream\Nwhere your father comes back to life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What I really love...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is to show people nightmares\Nright after a happy dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I just adore the sight\Nof a distorted human face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I get such a kick out of that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How enthralling is it to gaze at someone\Nshattered by misfortune, suffering and flailing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't usually let my guard down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, it may take longer,\Nbut I'll make sure to kill the Demon Slayers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mixed my blood\Nwith the ink on the tickets.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once the conductor punches them,\Ncreating clamp marks...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the spell activates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a remote art.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It took more effort, but this was\Nthe best way to avoid being detected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not being detected is important.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is reality for them\Nuntil they realize it's a dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}how did this one manage to wake up?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}And he found the way to wake up in a short time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Even though the human desire for blissful dreams,\Nfor self-serving dreams...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is so enormous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare intrude on my soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}What's that? I see he's wearing earrings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How lucky is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, he came right to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is like a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can receive\Neven more blood of Master Muzan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And once I become more powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll challenge an Upper Rank demon\Nto a duel to replace him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Water Breathing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tenth Form...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Constant Flux!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blood Demon Art!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whispers of Forced Unconscious Hypnosis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's not falling asleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Go... to... sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not working. But why not?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}No, that's not what this is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's falling under this spell over and over!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's aware that he's under the spell right away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}And he's committing suicide\Nin order to awaken!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if it's in the middle of a dream,\Nto commit suicide...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to take his own life with his own hands...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that takes incredible willpower!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This brat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}is insane!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing\Nwhile we were being murdered?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How could you be the only one to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think you were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're so useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It should've been you that died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you go on living\Nwithout a care?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way they'd ever say that!\NNot ever! Not my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,insult...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was way too easy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could this be a dream, too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or was this demon weaker than him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can totally see why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he ordered me to kill you,\Nthe boy with the earrings,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,along with the Hashira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your very existence is, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be more irritating, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's not dying?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that look on your face is so delightful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the look I've been wanting to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know why I'm not dead\Nafter you decapitated me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, since I'm feeling so ecstatic right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's so easy\Neven an infant would understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because the body over there\Nwas no longer my main body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Same with this thing\Nthat's talking to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It merely looks like my head, but it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,While you were snoozing away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}MUGEN
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I fused with this train!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every inch of this train has become\Nmy blood, my flesh and my bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you getting it now?\NIn other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the more than 200 passengers\Non this train...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are the food that will strengthen\Nmy body even more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as well as my hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you think\Nyou can protect them by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All these people packing this train\Nfrom one end to the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Can you alone keep me\Nfrom devouring them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do? What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}The most I can protect on my own is two cars!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Any more than that,\Nand I can't guarantee their safety!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rengoku! Zenitsu! Inosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be sleeping!\NWake up, will you? Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nezuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Protect the sleeping passengers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me, damn minions!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Explosive Awakening!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Comin' through!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Inosuke's comin' through!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beast Breathing, Fifth Fang...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crazy Cutting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Lord Inosuke Hashibira is comin' through!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inosuke, I'm so glad you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I came!\NI'm the boss, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's time for a Taisho-era secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.11,0:23:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inosuke's Kasugai Crow\Nis named Dongurimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's always by Inosuke's side,\Nbut he nearly got eaten by him,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so now I hear that he's staying invisible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inosuke, I'm really counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so bossy!\NYou're just an underling!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You make me feel so secure\Nwhen you're around, Inosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me feel so warm and fuzzy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Monjiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Episode 5, "Move Forward!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TO BE CONTINUED
